b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":1625,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding Adjustments to the Adventurer Vice","message":"<div>As part of the balance adjustments made to dragons and adventurers in the Version 2.0.0 update, the power of the adventurer Vice&#39;s skills after unlocking his mana spiral was adjusted downward before balance adjustments were applied.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>This action was taken upon determination that Vice&#39;s performance after unlocking his mana spiral, if left as-is, may adversely impact the game&#39;s balance and play experience even after the adjustments made in Version 2.0.0.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The adjustments are detailed below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Adjustments<\/div><div>\\u30fbDecreased shadow damage dealt by Fatal Blow Lv. 4 and added an effect that inflicts poison.<\/div><div>\\u30fbDecreased shadow damage dealt by Lethal Edge Lv. 3.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>As a goodwill gesture for these adjustments, affected players will be sent two Champion&#39;s Testaments and all players will be sent 600 wyrmite.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Affected players<\/div><div>Players who unlocked Vice&#39;s mana spiral before the release of Version 2.0.0<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Goodwill Gesture for affected players<\/div><div>Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 2<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Goodwill Gesture for all players<\/div><div>Wyrmite &times; 600<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for your understanding.<\/div>","start_time":1601002800,"prev_article_id":"1618","next_article_id":"1629","image_path":"","update_time":1600933513}}}'